reviewText: Hi i luv the gazette their music rocks.ruki so emotional talks quite a bit the only disappointing part is NO english subtitles. I was very bummed out but i didn't quite bother me i was listining to them play i enjoyed it very much...i just wish it had english subs....
excellent product on time all perfect

Of course I'm biased because I originally liked this band, but this concert was very special with a behind the scenes look at the previous concerts in the tour in the third disc. I can't get over how much I enjoy it XD
